<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>UTF-8 Converter Pro</title>
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:'Courier New',monospace;
     background:#0d0d0d;color:#e0e0e0;
     padding:20px}
h1{color:#00ff41;text-align:center;
   padding:20px;border:1px solid #1e3a1e;
   margin-bottom:20px}
nav{background:#111;border:1px solid #1e3a1e;
    padding:10px;margin-bottom:20px;
    text-align:center}
nav a{color:#ffb000;text-decoration:none;
      margin:0 15px;font-size:14px}
nav a:hover{color:#00ff41}
.card{background:#111;border:1px solid #1e3a1e;
      border-radius:6px;padding:20px;
      margin-bottom:20px}
h2{color:#ffb000;margin-bottom:15px}
label{color:#ffb000;font-size:13px;
      display:block;margin-bottom:5px}
input,textarea{width:100%;background:#0a0a0a;
  border:1px solid #1e3a1e;color:#00ff41;
  font-family:'Courier New',monospace;
  font-size:13px;padding:10px;
  border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:10px}
button{background:#0a0a0a;
       border:1px solid #00ff41;
       color:#00ff41;
       font-family:'Courier New',monospace;
       font-size:13px;padding:8px 20px;
       border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer}
button:hover{background:#1a2a1a}
.result{background:#080808;
        border:1px solid #1a2a1a;
        border-radius:4px;padding:15px;
        margin-top:15px}
.ok{color:#00ff41}
.err{color:#ff4444}
.hex{color:#ffb000}
.info{color:#00e5ff}
table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;
      font-size:13px}
th{color:#ffb000;text-align:left;
   padding:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #1e3a1e}
td{padding:6px 8px;
   border-bottom:1px solid #0f1f0f}
.footer{text-align:center;color:#555;
        font-size:11px;margin-top:20px}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>UTF-8 CONVERTER PRO<br>
<small style="font-size:13px;color:#555">
Django 6.0 + Python 3.14.2</small></h1>

<nav>
<a href="/comparaison/"
   style="color:#ff79c6">
  Comparaison
</a>
  <a href="/">Accueil</a>
  <a href="/encoder/">Encoder</a>
  <a href="/decoder/">Decoder</a>
  <a href="/analyser/">Analyser</a>
  <a href="/stats/">Stats</a>
</nav>


<div class="card">
  <h2>Bienvenue !</h2>
  <p style="color:#e0e0e0;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:15px">
    Convertisseur UTF-8 complet —
    encodez, decodez et analysez
    des caracteres Unicode.
  </p>
  <div style="display:grid;
              grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
              gap:15px">
    <a href="/encoder/"
       style="display:block;background:#0a0a0a;
              border:1px solid #00ff41;
              color:#00ff41;padding:15px;
              text-decoration:none;
              border-radius:4px;
              text-align:center">
      [1] ENCODER<br>
      <small style="color:#555">
        Texte vers UTF-8 hex</small>
    </a>
    <a href="/decoder/"
       style="display:block;background:#0a0a0a;
              border:1px solid #00e5ff;
              color:#00e5ff;padding:15px;
              text-decoration:none;
              border-radius:4px;
              text-align:center">
      [2] DECODER<br>
      <small style="color:#555">
        UTF-8 hex vers texte</small>
    </a>
    <a href="/analyser/"
       style="display:block;background:#0a0a0a;
              border:1px solid #ffb000;
              color:#ffb000;padding:15px;
              text-decoration:none;
              border-radius:4px;
              text-align:center">
      [3] ANALYSER<br>
      <small style="color:#555">
        Analyse d un caractere</small>
    </a>
    <a href="/stats/"
       style="display:block;background:#0a0a0a;
              border:1px solid #ff79c6;
              color:#ff79c6;padding:15px;
              text-decoration:none;
              border-radius:4px;
              text-align:center">
      [4] STATS<br>
      <small style="color:#555">
        Statistiques UTF-8</small>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="footer">
  UTF-8 Converter Pro — Python 3.14.2
</div>
</body>
</html>